Install each application package using iTunes or Apple Configurator on iPhone 6, 6s, 7 and 8 devices.

RECOMMENDATION: Unzip, then verify, each iOS application package.

Do so by opening a terminal application and typing, for example:
$ codesign -d --extract-certificates latest-2.4.ipa && \
openssl x509 -noout -fingerprint -sha256 -inform DER -in codesign0

Check the fingerprint:
9B:96:61:03:B0:C5:E1:F8:35:96:F7:B1:45:C0:3C:31:93:60:FD:21:03:A9:4C:1B:27:46:D9:9D:84:13:57:18